">Tate McRae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/parcels">Parcels</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Zedd">Zedd</a> 、Charlotte de Witte、 <a href="/artists/Teddy-Swims">Teddy Swims</a> 、 <a href="/artists/The-Marias">The Marías</a> 、Mon Laferte、 <a href="/artists/Fontaines-DC">Fontaines DC</a>等人登上舞台。在他们的周末。</p><p>智利版将于 3 月 21 日至 23 日周末在圣地亚哥 Bicentenario de Cerrillos 公园举行。您可以<a href="http://www.lollapaloozacl.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>购买节日门票。阿根廷版音乐盛典将于同一个周末在布宜诺斯艾利斯的 Hippodromo de San Isidro 举行。您可以<a href="http://www.lollapaloozaar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里购买门票</a>。巴西版将于 3 月 28 日至 30 日在圣保罗的 Autódromo de Interlagos 举行。您可以<a href="http://lollapaloozabr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>购买节日门票。</p><p>请查看以下 Lollapalooza 2025 南美版的完整阵容： </p><figure id="attachment_3791014" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791014" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791014" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Lollapalooza 巴西阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lollapalooza-Brasil-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791014" class="wp-caption-text"> Lollapalooza 巴西阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption><